15:10.743 --> 15:13.479
How's your tribute
to Cyril coming along, Ralph?

15:13.479 --> 15:15.648
Oh fine, fine.

15:15.648 --> 15:17.683
Let me read you
what I've got so far.

15:17.683 --> 15:19.818
When all
is said and done,

15:19.818 --> 15:21.220
one can honestly say,

15:21.220 --> 15:25.591
that Cyril Sneer
was truly, truly...

15:25.591 --> 15:28.560
Yes?
That's as far as I got.

15:28.560 --> 15:30.496
Do you think it's too long?

15:30.496 --> 15:32.932
Aaah!
Bert, are you alright?

15:32.932 --> 15:35.501
You look absolutely exhausted.

15:38.437 --> 15:40.773
Well, I am a little tired.

15:40.773 --> 15:41.941
I think
it would be best

15:41.941 --> 15:43.776
if you went to bed right away.

15:43.776 --> 15:45.577
No time, Melissa.

15:45.577 --> 15:47.446
I'm working the next shift.

15:48.948 --> 15:51.750
Hmm.. What is he up to?

15:53.052 --> 15:54.853
No, I don't wanna
buy any of that stock!

15:54.853 --> 15:56.455
Who is it?!

15:56.455 --> 15:58.924
It's me, Bert Raccoon.

15:58.924 --> 16:00.459
Well get...

16:00.459 --> 16:02.861
...in here right away.

16:02.861 --> 16:06.765
I-I feel I'm fading fast.

16:06.765 --> 16:10.803
Ohh Bert, Bert Raccoon?

16:10.803 --> 16:12.938
Is that you?

16:12.938 --> 16:16.942
My eyes, they're
so old and feeble.

16:18.277 --> 16:22.081
I'm afraid I've got
some bad news for you, Cyril.

16:22.081 --> 16:23.983
Bad news?

16:23.983 --> 16:27.086
I'm doing
everything I can,

16:27.086 --> 16:28.587
but even at this rate,

16:28.587 --> 16:31.123
I won't be able to
get the monument

16:31.123 --> 16:33.092
for at least a month!

16:33.092 --> 16:34.259
A month?!

16:34.259 --> 16:36.462
It just doesn't
look like I'm going to get

16:36.462 --> 16:38.731
all the money together in time.

16:38.731 --> 16:41.567
Nonsense!
Uh, I mean...

16:41.567 --> 16:43.535
Perhaps I can help you out.

16:45.504 --> 16:46.672
Will this do the trick?

16:48.974 --> 16:50.943
I'll say!

16:50.943 --> 16:54.513
And it'll help buy the plaque
I thought I'd never get!

16:54.513 --> 16:58.584
Telling the whole world
all about Cyril Sneer.

16:58.584 --> 17:01.353
Will it be ready
for the tribute tonight?

17:01.353 --> 17:04.123
Tonight?! Tonight?

17:04.123 --> 17:09.294
Yes, I plan the last
gathering with my close friends.

17:09.294 --> 17:11.363
So you must hurry, Bert.

17:11.797 --> 17:15.334
Hurry. My time is almost up.

17:15.334 --> 17:17.603
The Pigs: Time for
the next cure, Sir.

17:17.603 --> 17:20.172
You see, I was right.

17:24.076 --> 17:25.377
The Pig: Back to the lab.

17:27.613 --> 17:29.848
I've done it!
Not only will that check

17:29.848 --> 17:32.851
guarantee me my statue
with a plaque,

17:32.851 --> 17:35.687
but that Raccoon has
spent all his savings!

17:35.687 --> 17:38.457
That printing press
and that newspaper

17:38.457 --> 17:40.359
are junkyard material!

17:45.831 --> 17:48.367
Ladies and gentlemen,

17:48.367 --> 17:51.036
we are gathered here
this evening

17:51.036 --> 17:53.138
for a sad occasion.

17:53.672 --> 17:56.442
To honor one of
Evergreen Forests'

17:56.442 --> 17:59.845
most venerable citizens.

17:59.845 --> 18:01.847
Won't you please welcome

18:01.847 --> 18:04.650
our distinguished
guest of honor,

18:04.650 --> 18:06.919
Cyril Sneer.

18:08.187 --> 18:09.955
Let the tributes begin.

18:11.590 --> 18:14.993
Ehm-ehm.
Ode to Cyril Sneer,

18:14.993 --> 18:16.562
by Ralph Raccoon.

18:17.229 --> 18:20.599
Four score and $7 billion
dollars ago,

18:20.599 --> 18:23.902
Cyril Sneer set forth
into the world...

18:23.902 --> 18:26.705
...we can honestly say

18:26.705 --> 18:30.342
that Cyril Sneer
was without a doubt,

18:30.342 --> 18:32.244
truly pink.

18:34.346 --> 18:35.347
Bravo!

18:35.948 --> 18:37.716
Wh-what a beautiful speech!

18:37.716 --> 18:39.351
Where is Bert?

18:39.351 --> 18:40.786
Ehm-ehm...

18:40.786 --> 18:44.022
We've heard about
Cyril Sneer in words.

18:44.022 --> 18:46.592
Now let's remember him
through pictures.

18:47.526 --> 18:48.627
Oops.

18:49.995 --> 18:53.098
Here is 5 year old
Cyril and his father.

18:53.098 --> 18:55.801
Dad is asking for an
advance on his allowance.

18:55.801 --> 19:00.105
At age 7, Cyril's family
moves to a new home.

19:00.105 --> 19:01.907
Cyril has evicted them.

19:01.907 --> 19:04.409
Ooh, I'm fading fast!

19:04.409 --> 19:06.812
Um, here's Cyril at 10,

19:06.812 --> 19:08.480
Cyril at 15,

19:08.480 --> 19:09.948
Cyril at 20,

19:09.948 --> 19:11.783
I'm fading faster!

19:11.783 --> 19:13.952
30, 40, 50...

