19:25.464 --> 19:27.065
It would be just like him,

19:27.065 --> 19:29.301
to skip town with my cash!

19:32.437 --> 19:34.139
And now, for the moment

19:34.139 --> 19:36.575
you've all been waiting for.

19:36.575 --> 19:38.810
It's about time!

19:38.810 --> 19:41.013
The Pigs: For another cure!

19:41.013 --> 19:44.016
The only thing that's
gonna be cured around here

19:44.016 --> 19:45.450
is you hams!

19:52.191 --> 19:55.160
Please excuse the interruption.
Do go on.

19:55.160 --> 19:56.995
Um-oh, okay.

19:58.297 --> 20:00.132
Cyril Sneer,

20:00.132 --> 20:03.302
responsible for so many
memorable moments

20:03.302 --> 20:05.304
in everybody's life.

20:05.304 --> 20:06.638
And responsible for...

20:06.638 --> 20:08.607
...your demise!

20:10.108 --> 20:13.178
Mr Sneer, you shouldn't
be running around like that.

20:13.178 --> 20:15.514
Ha-ha, I've
never felt better!

20:15.514 --> 20:16.949
You're not dying?!

20:16.949 --> 20:19.117
Dying?
The only death knells

20:19.117 --> 20:22.120
that'll be ringing around here
are for your newspaper.

20:22.120 --> 20:25.724
Your monument to me has
put you out of business.

20:25.724 --> 20:26.725
Ha-haaa!

20:28.160 --> 20:29.328
Oooh!

20:29.328 --> 20:31.463
It's a new
printing press!

20:32.664 --> 20:35.000
It was thanks
to your generosity,

20:35.000 --> 20:37.002
that I got idea, Cyril.

20:37.002 --> 20:39.338
You let me look
around your library,

20:39.338 --> 20:41.840
and there, it hit me!

20:41.840 --> 20:44.876
That the printed
word is handed down

20:44.876 --> 20:47.179
from generation to generation.

20:47.179 --> 20:49.381
It lasts forever!

20:50.082 --> 20:52.818
So, this is our tribute to you!

20:52.818 --> 20:55.254
The Cyril Sneer

20:55.254 --> 20:57.522
Memorial Printing Press!

21:04.863 --> 21:05.497
Gee, Bert, that was awfully

21:05.497 --> 21:08.267
Gee, Bert, that was
awfully thoughtful of you,

21:08.267 --> 21:10.569
