a printing press.

21:10.569 --> 21:12.104
Aaah, I was only doing

21:12.104 --> 21:14.473
what I thought
was best for everyone,

21:14.473 --> 21:16.608
Cyril Sneer included.

21:17.276 --> 21:20.612
Ah, well, I'm exhausted.

21:20.612 --> 21:23.548
Good night, Bert!
Good night, guys.

21:28.453 --> 21:30.789
The Cyril Sneer
Memorial Printing Press,

21:30.789 --> 21:33.091
would toil on for years.

21:33.091 --> 21:35.961
Yet, no matter how greasy
or soiled it got,

21:35.961 --> 21:39.531
